   <taskbody>
      <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Before you can release a lock on a document, it must be checked out. Releasing a lock reverts the check-out of the document you are working on <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">without checking it in</i>. You can only release a lock when you have the document open in X-Author.</p>
      </context>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">From the X-Author pane, click on the <image placement="inline"
                      width="16"
                      href="../attachments/45220101/49676309.png"
                      id="image_cp1_gkn_12c"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
               <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Lock Status</uicontrol> tab icon.</cmd>
            <stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">The Lock Status page shows agreement details and information on the current
                  document lock.</p>
               <fig id="fig_lgl_r4j_12c" class="- topic/fig ">
                  <image height="400"
                         placement="break"
                         href="../attachments/45220101/49676310.png"
                         id="image_mgl_r4j_12c"
                         class="- topic/image "/>
               </fig>
            </stepresult>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Release Lock</uicontrol> on the Lock Status page.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">If you chose to release the lock, the document check-out is reverted. Any changes
               you made while the document was checked out are not saved.</cmd>
            <stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult ">
               <p class="- topic/p "> The page refreshes to reflect unlocked status and most menu options are
                  disabled.</p>
               <fig id="fig_px2_m2q_12c" class="- topic/fig ">
                  <image height="400"
                         placement="break"
                         href="../attachments/45220101/49676311.png"
                         id="image_rx2_m2q_12c"
                         class="- topic/image "/>
               </fig>
            </stepresult>
         </step>
      </steps>
      <postreq class="- topic/section task/postreq ">
         <note type="note" class="- topic/note ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">If you release a document lock in error and want to continue working with the document, go to the Lock Status page and click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Acquire Lock</uicontrol>.</p>
         </note>
      </postreq>
